{
  "stem": "1828.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of these silly things you never forget.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but we all were let through, the children and everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Soon enough, this SS man made a speech to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said that we are a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are show camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all the dignitaries that were going to come from everywhere, they were going to show him our camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that they are-- the children are going to be entertained during the day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were going to be all kinds of tasks for the-- for the men, and that we are to behave ourselves and to follow instructions, and nothing will happen to us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was already very different again, because they didn't shave our hair, the women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we saw the next--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We saw-- we had-- had reports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw the-- the women in the next enclosure who were speaking Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were-- it-- it was beyond description what you saw there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- all our clothes was taken from us with the goodies in it, the coins and whatever to save our lives.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- they-- the explanation for it was that they had to de-louse us because we are lousy Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're all full of stuff.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they gave us clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was assigned a little pile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything was taken away that we had worn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was very different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were allowed a-- a message to write with our tattooed number on it as a reference number, 30 words in capital letters, to whoever we wanted to write to.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, because of the [NON-ENGLISH], because of my organization, we had contact points.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a-- one half-Jew who belonged to our group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His father was a-- a Gentile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The mother was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was an engineer.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
